                  => 'DescriptionTool @5323c1ac-37e7-4acb-85ef-da870a700185 
                  {
                    activation = "activationRequested", 
                    author = "Paul-Ernest Martin", 
                    documentation = "Template to Facilitate The Link Between Random System et MIDI controleur.

Organisation : 

N- > Bank : 
     - Midi Pocket Avtivation : enables to desactiavte links between midi to intern parameters
     - BPMx5 : to link to BPMx5 to enabmes to this mode
      - Energy Chgt Detcetor : to link to a Ernergy Chgt Detector to enable this mode.
	   -  UI Trigger : to update description
   - WeakPointer to RS to fill enables to have complete description. 
    
Random System Inter Trigger : Intermediare Banks

Links Banks :
   - Pcket TO Rs : link directly from MDI to parametrs 
    - IMPORTANT : Triggers to link to the Trigger of the Random System you want to animate  IMPORTANT 

Ui RS Report"
                  }, 
